@s12 "2026-04-24T05:50:00Z"|"P35+"|"boundary_phase_census_complete"|"prior witness (additive row) next_probe[a] — enumerate all boundary phases"|"6 boundary phases (P11, P13, P17, P20, P22, P29) 전부 foundation-algebra 로 decompose — phase numbering 이 random 이 아닌 foundation 수식에 의해 결정됨을 재확인."|[{"phase":"P11","value":11,"title":"engine manifest + version stamping","decomp":"n + sopfr = 6 + 5","semantic":"foundation + prime-ingredients = manifest identity primitive"},{"phase":"P13","value":13,"title":"audit trail consumer + continuity claim","decomp":"sigma + mu = 12 + 1","semantic":"foundation + identity = self-awareness (reflective transition)","verified":"R24+10"},{"phase":"P17","value":17,"title":"claim schema completeness","decomp":"sigma + sopfr = 12 + 5","semantic":"foundation + prime-ingredients = structural schema","verified":"R24+10"},{"phase":"P20","value":20,"title":"engine source-hash stamp (tamper evidence)","decomp":"sigma + phi·tau = 12 + 8","semantic":"foundation + (gate·space product) = tamper-detection cage"},{"phase":"P22","value":22,"title":"reports emitter registry (orphan detection)","decomp":"sigma + n + tau = 12 + 6 + 4","semantic":"foundation + Banach + declaration-spaces = full coverage (first dual pair start)"},{"phase":"P29","value":29,"title":"manifest phase id monotonicity","decomp":"2·sigma + sopfr = 24 + 5","semantic":"doubled-foundation + prime-ingredients = strong structural enforcement"}]|"structural_numbering_theorem"|3|"All 6 gate-introducing boundary phases of n6-engine have non-trivial decompositions using foundation constants under {+, ·, ^}. Phase numbering is determined by foundation algebra, not chronological convenience."|"6/6 decomposition — pattern robust. 이제 '다음 boundary phase 가 어디 나올지' 예측 가능: foundation 산술로 미리 계산."|"R24+11. Functor F 의 semiring preservation (R24+10) 에서 Corollary 도출: engine 의 structural 숫자 자체 (phase index 포함) 가 foundation algebra 의 Concrete instance. '왜 특정 phase 가 P13, P17 에 land 하는가' 는 디자인 선택 아닌 수학적 필연."|"(